<h1> Programming Languages </h1>
<article class= "language">
<h2> C Language </h2>
<p> "The C programming language is a general-purpose, procedural, and imperative computer programming language developed in the early 1970s by Dennis Ritchie at Bell Labs." </p>
</article>
<article class= "language">
<h2> C++ Language </h2>
<p> "C++ is a powerful, general-purpose, and multi-paradigm programming language developed by Bjarne Stroustrup in 1979 as an extension of the C language." </p>
